{"tid":519523,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] Soccer Manager Arena 其實唔難 [2]","createTime":"2018-01-04T12:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T02:31:22.000Z","uid":157501,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"86248016e8272cb7ff4bf30f49b6998fefb9ef58","tid":519523,"uid":157501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:24:20.000Z","msg":"重新整理完重新開一次<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">呢隻其實唔係新game <br />\n不過仍然有可玩之處，而且唔會話早玩屈晒機，同埋你唔會有追唔到既感覺<br />\n0課慢慢玩就可以 </span><br />\n5人足球game 控波傳波射波通通任你操作<br />\n唔同球員有唔同技能 可以睇準時機發動<br />\n<br />\n雖然球員有技能，我相信有d巴打會同我一樣覺得有技既足球game係唔真實<br />\n會唔會半場就射入<br />\n呢隻未至於咁誇張，要真正易入一定要入到禁區，所以其實係有一定難度！<br />\n<br />\n遊戲實際操作︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZJRJ_bN6_Do\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZJRJ_bN6_Do&d=hA8a%2BddWznd2NUoDpJQQ06WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=cbba6e83\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZJRJ_bN6_Do</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Club︰LIHKG</span></span><br />\n唔想入Club 既都可以入TG傾 ︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/GU-sUkpN0ntodbf5I8afGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FGU-sUkpN0ntodbf5I8afGQ&d=hA8a%2BddWznd2NUoDpJQQ06WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=27f7c44d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/GU-sUkpN0ntodbf5I8afGQ</a><br />\n入左Club 既巴打記得係下面留名 (我主要睇呢個list黎踢人 )︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1NE-QMzzDUzwec78b7exey0q848mMtVOSi7xcrNmUb-c/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1NE-QMzzDUzwec78b7exey0q848mMtVOSi7xcrNmUb-c%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=hA8a%2BddWznd2NUoDpJQQ06WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=2cbc6e76\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1NE-QMzzDUzwec78b7exey0q848mMtVOSi7xcrNmUb-c/edit#gid=0</a><br />\n球員Data︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Btz1OKp1nO09hgwf7kJgcjep3W6U2LUVs168povERDU/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1Btz1OKp1nO09hgwf7kJgcjep3W6U2LUVs168povERDU%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=hA8a%2BddWznd2NUoDpJQQ06WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=4f7eafa7\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Btz1OKp1nO09hgwf7kJgcjep3W6U2LUVs168povERDU/edit#gid=0</a><br />\n<br />\nFAQ︰<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">問︰</span>駛唔駛首抽?<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">答︰</span>首先先講我自己係冇首抽下直接玩，但有冇首抽呢？係有，一開始個包金pack係必定出綠所以唔駛期待，當你完成晒教學入到去抽卡個版，右上感嘆號個包登入包係可以開到Koke 紫卡！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">問︰</span>卡點分勁定廢？<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">答︰</span>綠&gt;藍&gt;紫&gt;傳奇，總共4個階段，但唔係一定用晒傳奇就係勁，因為要考慮到出技次數<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">問︰</span>咩係出技次數？<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">答︰</span>出技次數係基於你既個人等級，越高級可用既越多次數，但目前我見manager 最高係9級，所以可能係有限最高等級，信我~如果你用最高級個d，半場就會用完。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">問︰</span>點防守？<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">答︰</span>當你防守球員同對面帶波球員重疊，你禁佢就會有challenge，tackle 高就會贏，但留意你贏一次體力就會扣一格，亦即係你果個球員既tackle就會按比例低左，所以你唔會贏足全場。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">問︰</span>點升球員等級？<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">答︰</span> 每種卡都有等級上限<br />\n綠卡︰10 ，藍卡︰8 ，紫卡︰5 傳奇︰未知 (未有巴打有)，開Pack只要開返果個球員就會有經驗，信我好易有<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">問︰</span>點拎League Pack？<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">答︰</span>只要League 玩Rank 就會計入入球，但當League開始左，你既入球將唔會計入在內，所以早d入Club吧啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2ab900166547b6a71713343d3425040097c056","tid":519523,"uid":42954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:32:07.000Z","msg":"新post留名"},{"pid":"ccc1410f95e3d0ae3197c1bc56f6647c35262072","tid":519523,"uid":51775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:42:33.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n推薦大家用stone <br />\n招技好勁"},{"pid":"36940bcd6e381b222e95bea68f1758501beaf94c","tid":519523,"uid":148742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201